Add Sprint 2: Senso, Airbyte, Overshoot integrations + monitoring

New services:
- senso_service: Context OS for grounded knowledge (search, generate, triggers, seed compliance docs)
- airbyte_service: Stripe billing anomaly detection + Slack alerts
- overshoot_service: Vision AI for financial broadcast monitoring

New router:
- /api/monitor/status — integration health check
- /api/monitor/scan — trigger manual scan across all sources
- /api/monitor/demo — pre-built detections for reliable demo

Background worker:
- worker/monitor.py — persistent monitoring loop for Render Background Worker

Wiring:
- search_task_context now queries Senso for verified policy guidance
- end_task now sends completion summary to Slack
- render.yaml updated with worker service + new env vars

